---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import CertificationFlow from '../components/react/CertificationFlow';
---

<Layout title="About Us - ABKHD Store">
  <Header slot="header" />
  
  <div class="container py-8 md:py-12">
    <!-- Navigation -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <nav class="flex items-center space-x-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-4">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-foreground">Home</a>
        <i class="bi bi-chevron-right"></i>
        <span class="text-foreground">About</span>
      </nav>
      <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card hover:border-primary/50 transition-colors">
        <i class="bi bi-arrow-left text-lg"></i>
        <span class="text-sm font-medium">Back to Home</span>
      </a>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Content Container -->
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <!-- SECTION 1: HERO - Emotional Hook -->
      <div class="text-center mb-16 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6">
          We've Been Cheated Too.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-primary font-semibold mb-4">
          That's exactly why ABKHD exists.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          I'm sure must people might have a similar story, i personally once bought a used mobile phone at our local gadget market. The phone looked good, but unbeknownst to me, it had a bad battery, overheated when connected to the internet, had been worked on by an inexperienced technician, and had many more issues. Long story short, the phone died just 2 days after I bought it.
          <br />
          <br />
          We built <span class="text-primary font-semibold">ABKHD</span> to be the store we wish existed when we were buyers.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- SECTION 2: OUR STORY - Single Condensed Card -->
      <div class="mb-20 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8">How Distrust Built Trust</h2>
        
        <div class="p-8 rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/50">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-center">
            <div>
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-red-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
                <i class="bi bi-x-circle text-red-500 text-2xl"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">The Problem</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
                Fake parts, dead devices, sellers who ghosted us after taking our money.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-orange-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
                <i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle text-orange-500 text-2xl"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">The Pattern</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
                Everyone we knew had horror stories. This was just "how things are."
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
                <i class="bi bi-arrow-right text-primary text-2xl"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">The Decision</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
                In 2024, ABKHD was born. A promise to do things differently.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- SECTION 3: TOP 2 NON-NEGOTIABLES -->
      <div class="mb-20 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-4">Our Non-Negotiables</h2>
        <p class="text-center text-muted-foreground mb-10">
          These aren't just values. They're commitments we make to every customer.
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <!-- Value 1: Radical Transparency -->
          <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/50 hover:border-primary transition-colors">
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-4 mb-4">
              <i class="bi bi-eye text-primary text-2xl mt-1"></i>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-1">Radical Transparency</h3>
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary">If it's broken, we'll tell you.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
              Every defect no matter how small is disclosed in the product description. Screenshots, photos, everything. You decide if it's a deal-breaker, not us.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Value 2: Real Warranties -->
          <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/50 hover:border-primary transition-colors">
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-4 mb-4">
              <i class="bi bi-shield-check text-primary text-2xl mt-1"></i>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-1">Real Warranties</h3>
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary">No fake promises.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
              If we offer a warranty, it's real and enforceable. No fine print loopholes. No ghosting after sale. We're on WhatsApp, we're here.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- SECTION 4: COMPARISON TABLE -->
      <div class="mb-20 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-4">How We're Different</h2>
        <p class="text-center text-muted-foreground mb-10">
          The contrast is clear. You decide who to trust.
        </p>
        
        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="w-full border-collapse">
            <thead>
              <tr class="border-b-2 border-border">
                <th class="p-4 text-left font-bold">Typical Sellers</th>
                <th class="p-4 text-left font-bold text-primary">ABKHD</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="text-sm">
              <tr class="border-b border-border hover:bg-muted/20 transition-colors">
                <td class="p-4">
                  <i class="bi bi-x-circle text-red-500 mr-2"></i>
                  <span class="text-muted-foreground">"UK-used" (source unknown)</span>
                </td>
                <td class="p-4">
                  <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-primary mr-2"></i>
                  <span>UK and China-sourced with verification</span>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-border hover:bg-muted/20 transition-colors">
                <td class="p-4">
                  <i class="bi bi-x-circle text-red-500 mr-2"></i>
                  <span class="text-muted-foreground">Hidden defects</span>
                </td>
                <td class="p-4">
                  <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-primary mr-2"></i>
                  <span>All defects disclosed with photos</span>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-border hover:bg-muted/20 transition-colors">
                <td class="p-4">
                  <i class="bi bi-x-circle text-red-500 mr-2"></i>
                  <span class="text-muted-foreground">Generic "warranty included"</span>
                </td>
                <td class="p-4">
                  <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-primary mr-2"></i>
                  <span>Specific, enforceable warranty terms</span>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-border hover:bg-muted/20 transition-colors">
                <td class="p-4">
                  <i class="bi bi-x-circle text-red-500 mr-2"></i>
                  <span class="text-muted-foreground">Disappear after sale</span>
                </td>
                <td class="p-4">
                  <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-primary mr-2"></i>
                  <span>WhatsApp support, always reachable</span>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-border hover:bg-muted/20 transition-colors">
                <td class="p-4">
                  <i class="bi bi-x-circle text-red-500 mr-2"></i>
                  <span class="text-muted-foreground">"Trust me, it works"</span>
                </td>
                <td class="p-4">
                  <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-primary mr-2"></i>
                  <span>Diagnostic reports and battery health shown</span>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="hover:bg-muted/20 transition-colors">
                <td class="p-4">
                  <i class="bi bi-x-circle text-red-500 mr-2"></i>
                  <span class="text-muted-foreground">Switched-off numbers after issues</span>
                </td>
                <td class="p-4">
                  <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-primary mr-2"></i>
                  <span>Permanent contact, we stand behind every sale</span>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- SECTION 5: CERTIFICATION PROCESS - Interactive Animation -->
      <div class="mb-20 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-3">How We Certify Every Device</h2>
        <p class="text-center text-muted-foreground mb-6">
          Our multi-point inspection ensures you get certified performance
        </p>
        
        <div class="p-6 md:p-8 rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/50">
          <CertificationFlow client:visible />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- SECTION 6: TESTING GRID -->
      <div class="mb-20 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-8">What We Test</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
          <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/50 hover:border-primary transition-colors">
            <i class="bi bi-battery-charging text-primary text-3xl mb-3"></i>
            <p class="text-sm font-medium">Battery Health</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-1">With diagnostics</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/50 hover:border-primary transition-colors">
            <i class="bi bi-display text-primary text-3xl mb-3"></i>
            <p class="text-sm font-medium">Screen Clarity</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-1">Every pixel checked</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/50 hover:border-primary transition-colors">
            <i class="bi bi-cpu text-primary text-3xl mb-3"></i>
            <p class="text-sm font-medium">Processor Speed</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-1">Performance tested</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/50 hover:border-primary transition-colors">
            <i class="bi bi-plug text-primary text-3xl mb-3"></i>
            <p class="text-sm font-medium">Port Function</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-1">All ports verified</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- SECTION 7: TEAM -->
      <div class="mb-20 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary text-sm font-medium mb-6">
            <i class="bi bi-people-fill mr-2"></i>
            Who We Are
          </span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Meet the Founders</h2>

          <span class="inline-flex items-center text-primary text-xl font-extrabold mb-6">
            ABKHD Store
          </span>

          <p class="text-muted-foreground max-w-xl mx-auto">
            Real people with real stakes in doing this right.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
          <!-- Team Member 1 -->
          <div class="group">
            <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden mb-6 aspect-[3/4] bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-100 to-slate-200">
              <img 
                src="https://res.cloudinary.com/cloudinary-lycan-xx/image/upload/v1772930158/team1_skylqx.jpg" 
                alt="Abubakar-Sadieq" 
                class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-105" 
              />
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-1">Abubakar-Sadieq Abdulazeez</h3>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium text-primary mb-2">Founder ABKHD</p>
              <p class="text-sm italic text-primary">
                "I have the connections and know the products."
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Team Member 2 -->
          <div class="group">
            <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden mb-6 aspect-[3/4] bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-100 to-slate-200">
              <img 
                src="https://res.cloudinary.com/cloudinary-lycan-xx/image/upload/v1772930160/team2_ofiswe.jpg" 
                alt="Abduljalal" 
                class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-105" 
              />
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-1">Abduljalal Muhammad</h3>
              <p class="text-sm italic text-primary">
                "The watchful eye that sees what dishonest sellers hide."
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Team Member 3 -->
          <div class="group">
            <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden mb-6 aspect-[3/4] bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-100 to-slate-200">
              <img 
                src="https://res.cloudinary.com/cloudinary-lycan-xx/image/upload/v1772930155/team3_hys08b.jpg" 
                alt="Mohammad" 
                class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-105" 
              />
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-1">Mohammad (Sani) Bello</h3>
              <p class="text-sm italic text-primary">
                "I am your typical tech. guy that bought the faulty phone."
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- SECTION 8: FINAL CTA -->
      <div class="text-center p-10 rounded-xl border-2 border-primary/30 bg-card/50 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-3">Ready to Buy Tech Without the Fear?</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-6 max-w-xl mx-auto">
          Join customers who've discovered what honest selling looks like. No games. No tricks. Just quality devices and real transparency.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/shop" class="btn-primary px-8 py-3">
            Browse Products
          </a>
          <a 
            href="https://wa.me/2348012345678" 
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 font-medium rounded-lg border-2 border-primary text-primary hover:bg-primary hover:text-primary-foreground transition-colors"
          >
            <i class="bi bi-whatsapp mr-2"></i>
            Contact Us on WhatsApp
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <Footer slot="footer" />
</Layout>